Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.87,0:00:04.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear they're back.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.22,0:00:06.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.78,0:00:11.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The core members of Fairy Tail \Nwho disappeared seven years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.24,0:00:12.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.85,0:00:15.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't fool me, Rogue.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.03,0:00:17.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember how you looked up to Natsu-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.32,0:00:21.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.09,0:02:01.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I admonish us all for our sins.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.15,0:02:06.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We, Zentopia, should repent for all \Nof the mistakes we've made up to now
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.70,0:02:09.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and begin walking upon a new path...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.03,0:02:12.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Only then may we purge our sins...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.86,0:02:14.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is tiring...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.57,0:02:16.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What can you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.18,0:02:18.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The archbishop himself invited us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.78,0:02:22.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but what about everybody else?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.33,0:02:25.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As if they'd come to a ceremony like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.06,0:02:30.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We Legionnaires...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.31,0:02:35.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...deeply apologize to you, Fairy Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.38,0:02:38.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, the crisis is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.24,0:02:40.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your heads.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.60,0:02:44.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We fought, but let that \Nbe water under the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.76,0:02:47.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start afresh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.43,0:02:49.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My gratitude knows no bounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.61,0:02:53.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.76,0:02:55.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...party time!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.92,0:03:01.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabertooth!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.98,0:03:07.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The battle over the Infinity Clock was over
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.33,0:03:10.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and the escaped members of Oracion Seis
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.64,0:03:13.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,had been returned to prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.25,0:03:14.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.29,0:03:15.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.80,0:03:20.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That puny guild was the \Ncause of all the trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.83,0:03:23.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What a total nuisance!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.13,0:03:26.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even remember the \Nname of that guild...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.92,0:03:29.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.97,0:03:33.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, the brave actions of Natsu \Nand the rest notwithstanding,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.41,0:03:37.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,the guild's reputation continued to plummet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.86,0:03:39.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.98,0:03:41.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, Neville's \NCelestial Spirit Wizards
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.86,0:03:44.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,have been awakened from the \N100-year sleeping spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.55,0:03:48.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,However, just as with Katja,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.33,0:03:53.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,all of them have lost their magic power and \Nare no longer Celestial Spirit Wizards.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.33,0:03:55.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.20,0:03:57.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as it says in the report.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.10,0:04:02.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're as they were seven years ago, \Nback home and as boisterous as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.48,0:04:06.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, so boisterous that the \NChairman is miffed about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.55,0:04:09.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You... You knew about this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.62,0:04:13.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It would have been easy \Nfor me to tell you, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.50,0:04:15.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.11,0:04:19.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.70,0:04:22.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.90,0:04:25.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And now, to celebrate the successful \Nconclusion of the latest crisis,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.60,0:04:28.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,an eating contest between \NNatsu and Dan... begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.70,0:04:30.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fired up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.31,0:04:31.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna win this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.01,0:04:35.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's as energetic as usual...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.32,0:04:38.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like that Infinity Clock \Nbusiness happened ages ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.38,0:04:40.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.99,0:04:42.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.71,0:04:44.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you get!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.15,0:04:45.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Isn't that against the rules?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.72,0:04:47.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, we'll allow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.60,0:04:52.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just think, right about now, Master \Nand Wakaba are listening to a sermon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.38,0:04:55.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know whether to say they're \Nsoft-hearted or just got the short end of the stick...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.44,0:04:59.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But that ceremony's a \Nbig deal to them, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.35,0:05:02.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So what's Legion doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.26,0:05:05.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're the same as you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.24,0:05:06.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For us, this is also...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.89,0:05:08.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.19,0:05:10.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, we're playing hooky!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.15,0:05:13.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure that's okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.02,0:05:17.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you take advantage of the chaos \Nhere and rub up against Gray-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.18,0:05:19.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Spicy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.16,0:05:21.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,These people are hard to \Ntalk to. Pain in the ass...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.70,0:05:24.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.27,0:05:26.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.74,0:05:28.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I ask again...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.07,0:05:30.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.85,0:05:34.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I said something terrible \Nto you that last time!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.51,0:05:36.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I said I hated cats... and...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.98,0:05:39.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's fine. Forget about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.90,0:05:43.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, even though you're a different \Nperson, I was still able to meet "Coco" again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.85,0:05:46.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's more than I could've asked for.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.01,0:05:47.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.02,0:05:51.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, from here on out, let's be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.17,0:05:52.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.06,0:05:54.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.83,0:05:56.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Before you start talking,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.73,0:05:59.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,would you have another bout with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.46,0:06:00.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.45,0:06:02.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.25,0:06:04.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.19,0:06:09.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.80,0:06:10.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.00,0:06:12.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.44,0:06:14.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.52,0:06:20.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That side of the room's kind of gloomy,  huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.35,0:06:24.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those two haven't said \Na word to each other...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.45,0:06:28.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a break. That's \Nno way to drink booze.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.75,0:06:47.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Is it just my imagination?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.63,0:06:49.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're smiling?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.20,0:06:55.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Our scrap left me numb.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.26,0:06:57.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's a wide world out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.03,0:07:00.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I never knew there were wizards like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.48,0:07:02.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was motivation and the luck of the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.19,0:07:05.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And there are a lot of other factors, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.86,0:07:12.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how it would turn out \Nif we ever locked horns again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.07,0:07:14.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You take a broad view of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.32,0:07:17.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I just live selfishly is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.08,0:07:18.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what they're talking about...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.83,0:07:22.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind. It's probably just dirty talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.30,0:07:25.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Lu-pi's not here...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.49,0:07:27.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you fixated on Angel last time?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.74,0:07:31.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Life is short, so it's a waste not to \Nlive it up with every chance you get.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.99,0:07:33.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.52,0:07:36.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the one who falls in \Nlove at the drop of a hat?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.11,0:07:40.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.77,0:07:43.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's scary! Help me, Er-pin!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.10,0:07:44.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Er... pin?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.85,0:07:46.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Scary...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.10,0:07:48.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm stayin' out of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.61,0:07:51.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew from the start how you felt about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.86,0:07:54.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's become a happy cou...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.10,0:07:57.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...ple...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.18,0:07:59.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can only take so much fickleness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.24,0:08:00.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I didn't warn you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.67,0:08:03.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Erza won with one blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.14,0:08:06.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the proper way to use the \Nweapon that keeps evil at bay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.32,0:08:12.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing out here by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.60,0:08:14.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.02,0:08:17.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.29,0:08:20.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After what I did to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.78,0:08:22.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,how can you smile at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.40,0:08:25.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.91,0:08:28.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And you Legionnaires were tricked, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.24,0:08:31.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.99,0:08:36.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Before Zentopia took me in,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.27,0:08:39.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd been tricked and used my whole life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.50,0:08:43.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But everything changed once I got power.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.47,0:08:48.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If it was for the sake of Zentopia, which \Nraised me to be a person with power,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.80,0:08:51.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I would do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.98,0:08:54.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking that, I controlled people...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.07,0:08:58.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And it felt like I was getting revenge \Non the people who had used me long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.64,0:09:02.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But in the end, I was \Nonly being used again...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.94,0:09:06.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We Legionnaires, His Grace, Rapowant, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.74,0:09:07.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And also...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.28,0:09:10.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...Michelle, who was with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.23,0:09:14.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems you've managed to \Ncast off your hesitancy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.28,0:09:16.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your movements are quite agile today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.57,0:09:19.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but not agile enough to beat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.67,0:09:22.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad, I wanted to beat \Nyou once in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.05,0:09:24.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.02,0:09:25.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Coco...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.92,0:09:31.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.63,0:09:34.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm holding something very heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.15,0:09:36.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.75,0:09:40.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Certainly, I have entrusted \Nyou with that golden seal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.92,0:09:43.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm not...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.39,0:09:47.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Though I was mind-controlled \Nthrough all of this,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.33,0:09:51.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,the weakness of my own mind \Nis partially to blame.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.36,0:09:56.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,From here on out, Legion's mission \Nis going to be a long, severe one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.08,0:09:59.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please make good use of that golden seal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.81,0:10:03.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Be it ever so little, try to \Nbring light to people's hearts...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.70,0:10:05.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your words are more than we deserve.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.70,0:10:10.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, what should Gatman-chama do...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.12,0:10:16.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We are responsible for sealing you away \Nin that prison in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.50,0:10:22.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, I would like you to use your \Nmagic to help rebuild the local parish.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.43,0:10:24.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do everything in my power!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.01,0:10:28.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, there is one thing \Nthat's been bothering me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.68,0:10:30.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.54,0:10:34.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The puppets that Rapowant \Nsent to every area...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.60,0:10:37.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We investigated closely and \Nfound out what he was up to...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.55,0:10:40.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...with the real Michelle Lobster.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.14,0:10:47.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, Rapowant had his eye on the \NLobster family fortune, so he kept her at hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.56,0:10:52.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, um, the official document showing she's \Na distant relative of the Heartfilia family...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.07,0:10:56.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a fake too, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.01,0:11:00.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I... wanted to apologize...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.21,0:11:05.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...so I went off in search of at least \Nsome good news I could tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.89,0:11:07.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...but it was all...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.38,0:11:09.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.16,0:11:14.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I suspected as much...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.66,0:11:16.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...so now it's off my chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.25,0:11:17.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.79,0:11:19.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.74,0:11:21.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel a little lonely...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.33,0:11:24.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I have friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.30,0:11:26.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.23,0:11:31.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, now that I'm refreshed, here...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.64,0:11:32.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's make up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.50,0:11:34.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shake.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.25,0:11:40.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, we'll start as friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.61,0:11:43.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think that line fits here...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.94,0:11:50.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We visited here today for one reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.22,0:11:53.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I realized.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.19,0:11:55.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,To say goodbye...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.91,0:11:57.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.52,0:11:59.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In accordance with His Grace's instructions,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.71,0:12:05.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,we Legionnaires are to seek out the \Nscattered parts of the Infinity Clock in every region
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.38,0:12:08.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and find a better way to seal them up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.49,0:12:12.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That being said, until the \Nparts accumulate magic power,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.59,0:12:14.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,it will be impossible to \Nlocate them with magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.18,0:12:18.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This work is going to last \Neach one of us a lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.40,0:12:24.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In all likelihood, this is the \Nlast time we'll be able to meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.61,0:12:25.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.63,0:12:27.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you sayin'?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.65,0:12:30.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's boring to jump to that \Nconclusion from the outset!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.72,0:12:31.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.06,0:12:34.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Coco... Thank you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.81,0:12:37.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mary, you stop by and \Nhang out again too, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.58,0:12:38.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank {\i1}you{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.06,0:12:41.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care, Princess, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.37,0:12:43.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I promise to come back! Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.47,0:12:46.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll see you again, Aniki.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.70,0:12:49.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can come over to challenge \Nme to a fight anytime... Sam.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.85,0:12:52.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? He hasn't called him that before...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.86,0:12:55.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's meet again somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.00,0:12:57.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that includes you too, Sugar Boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.46,0:12:58.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dan...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.61,0:13:02.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Learn how to stick with one person.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.30,0:13:05.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a hot message! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.57,0:13:07.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, 'til we meet again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.62,0:13:09.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.51,0:13:12.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, octopus man! \NIt almost slipped my mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.84,0:13:14.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"Octopus man"...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.49,0:13:15.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.13,0:13:20.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't scowling all the time make you \Ntired? You oughta try a smile once in a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.46,0:13:21.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.98,0:13:25.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.00,0:13:27.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After all this time, it \Nwould be out of character...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.45,0:13:29.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He very rarely smiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.31,0:13:35.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can face my heart head on...\N Wasn't that it, Coco?{smp: this is really weird to parse. Can it be "If I can face my heart directly..."?}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.50,0:13:43.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally understand what you said that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.40,0:13:49.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Eww!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.05,0:13:52.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can tell he's totally \Nnot used to doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.74,0:13:56.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Byro-sama, that's actually scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.11,0:13:58.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that, you rascals?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.70,0:14:04.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And with laughter in the air, \Nthey began their journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.78,0:14:09.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure we'll meet again sometime...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.95,0:14:24.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Master Org, thank you for your \Nhard work at the Council meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.37,0:14:26.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.46,0:14:30.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Has the Guild Amity and Trade Treaty \Nreform bill been decided on yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.61,0:14:31.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.51,0:14:35.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,you've already heard, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.85,0:14:38.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,About the return of Fairy \NTail's main members...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.83,0:14:41.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For political reasons,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.41,0:14:46.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,the chairman apparently intends to tie in \Nthe Infinity Clock and Oracion Seis affair
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.32,0:14:50.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,not with Zentopia but with {\i1}their{\i0} return...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.16,0:14:55.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's fine. As long \Nas the case is closed...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.87,0:15:00.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The magic world may be in \Nfor troubled times again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.29,0:15:05.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened this time may \Nonly have been a harbinger.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.06,0:15:10.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been seven years since \NAcnologia and Zeref awoke...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.45,0:15:14.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. We still haven't been \Nable to find either one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.13,0:15:18.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps we should augment \Nthe expeditionary force.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.06,0:15:22.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been too quiet these past seven years.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.67,0:15:26.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're keeping an eye on Sabertooth's ascent,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.39,0:15:29.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but Tartaros hasn't made any noticeable moves
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.51,0:15:32.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and the same goes for the remaining \Nmembers of Grimoire Heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.87,0:15:36.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And we have no information \Non Zeref or Acnologia.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.50,0:15:40.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,However, it's an eerie silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.12,0:15:44.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like an endless night.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.61,0:15:49.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Will it be sunrise soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.64,0:15:53.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Will it become a great \Ndawn for the magic world?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.97,0:15:57.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And you think Fairy Tail will set it off?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.43,0:16:05.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I despised Fairy Tail before and here \NI am expecting something of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.90,0:16:08.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I must be getting old.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.65,0:16:15.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabertooth?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.35,0:16:18.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabertooth, as in the tigers with \Nthe saber-like canine teeth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.10,0:16:23.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They've surpassed Pegasus and Lamia and are \Ncurrently the strongest wizards' guild in Fiore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.11,0:16:24.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Never heard of 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.68,0:16:27.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They hadn't made much of \Na splash seven years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.48,0:16:30.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then they've suddenly risen to prominence \Nthese past seven years, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.70,0:16:32.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What did it was changing their guild master
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.96,0:16:37.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and the induction of five extremely \Npowerful wizards into their ranks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.05,0:16:40.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Things can change that much \Nwith just five people?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.49,0:16:41.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They got some guts.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.99,0:16:45.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Incidentally, how is our guild ranked?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.52,0:16:46.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna ask that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.83,0:16:49.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wendy, there's no need to rub it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.98,0:16:51.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're bottom-ranked.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.14,0:16:52.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're a totally wimpy guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.69,0:16:54.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The weakest guild in Fiore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.36,0:16:56.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.10,0:17:00.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's even better! It's more fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.15,0:17:02.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.33,0:17:06.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Think of how much fun it's \Ngonna be climbin' to the top again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.22,0:17:07.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fired up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.75,0:17:08.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeesh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.50,0:17:11.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm no match for Natsu-nii.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.75,0:17:14.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right! Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.40,0:17:15.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking forward to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.67,0:17:17.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.65,0:17:19.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you seen Gildarts?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.26,0:17:23.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What, do you get lonely \Nwhen Papa's not around?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.53,0:17:24.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.08,0:17:26.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.20,0:17:29.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's okay. Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.87,0:17:33.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's consoling Gray-sama?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.80,0:17:37.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gildarts went with Master to the \Noriginal Fairy Tail base of operations.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.40,0:17:40.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Then I'll go out on \Na job while I have the chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.95,0:17:44.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's amazing how lovey-dovey \NGildarts gets with Cana.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.77,0:17:47.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You fawn over Carla the same way...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.25,0:17:50.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And he's supposed to be \Nthe guild's strongest...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.65,0:17:52.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is such an oddball guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.41,0:17:57.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure we can just go in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.45,0:18:00.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The building was repossessed, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.56,0:18:02.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll get it back soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.77,0:18:05.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I didn't know about this...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.45,0:18:08.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A deep underground passage below the guild...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.77,0:18:11.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because I didn't \Ntell anybody about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.38,0:18:12.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And why's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.01,0:18:15.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you'll understand when you see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.99,0:18:20.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.28,0:18:27.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.94,0:18:46.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Our guild's greatest secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.44,0:18:52.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lumen Histoire...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.53,0:19:02.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?! What does it mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.42,0:19:08.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mavis wrote that this is \NFairy Tail's true nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.37,0:19:12.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I can't find the words...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.67,0:19:14.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't blame you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.36,0:19:17.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When Purehito showed this to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.33,0:19:19.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,words failed me as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.91,0:19:22.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is something like this below the guild?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.74,0:19:24.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And why show me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.54,0:19:30.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you're going to be \Nthe next Fairy Tail master...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.85,0:19:32.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...Gildarts!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.56,0:19:52.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gildarts! It's been too long, let's fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.22,0:19:59.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like Natsu is a bug \Nthat pesters people...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.96,0:20:07.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell, Gildarts? \NYou're in a bad mood, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.48,0:20:10.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right? I'm always like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.15,0:20:12.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.86,0:20:15.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.25,0:20:20.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This makes me feel nostalgic.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.76,0:20:24.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Seven years ago, I was like this tall.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.19,0:20:29.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You were a fan of Gajeel-san, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.90,0:20:32.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, Gajeel-san was scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.53,0:20:34.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let yourself be \Nbound by the past, Sting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.03,0:20:37.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They weren't on the path we took.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.49,0:20:40.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Found 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.76,0:20:43.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.43,0:20:51.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Eating... an arrow?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.06,0:20:56.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me he...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.28,0:21:11.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Maybe I'm rusty...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.90,0:21:13.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I missed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.88,0:21:16.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It was you two?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.45,0:21:19.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Twin Dragons of Sabertooth...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.87,0:21:23.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,White Dragon, Sting and Shadow Dragon, Rogue!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.70,0:21:26.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Dragon Slayer duo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.05,0:21:30.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.73,0:21:32.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna leave your friends here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.90,0:21:34.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You suck!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.05,0:21:39.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you expect from a Dark Guild?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.98,0:21:43.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You blew things up really \Ngood again, huh, Sting-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.86,0:21:46.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lecter and Frosch, where were you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.22,0:21:50.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, just doing a little reconnoitering...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.53,0:21:55.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Y'know, the Fire Dragon, Iron Dragon, heck, \Neven the Sky Dragon don't stand a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.58,0:21:58.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got it goin' on, oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.60,0:22:00.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fro thinks so, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.39,0:22:01.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.69,0:22:07.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sting-kun, you're the strongest \NDragon Slayer, oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.05,0:22:11.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The way I am now, I'm positive \NI could beat Natsu-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.26,0:22:14.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.06,0:22:17.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you say we challenge them, Rogue?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.42,0:22:19.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.10,0:22:20.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fro neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.45,0:23:58.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, did you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.00,0:24:01.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a festival to decide \Nthe #1 guild in Fiore!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.22,0:24:05.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Grand Magic Games, right? \NWe're gonna win for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.38,0:24:09.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When even fighting Max is a hard \Nbattle...? Are you gonna be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.22,0:24:11.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll build myself up by the \Ntime the tournament starts!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.33,0:24:13.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fired up!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.47,0:24:16.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: And So, We Aim for the Top!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.43,0:24:21.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you gonna do if it's not a \Nbattle but a quiz that takes brains?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.97,0:24:24.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, I'll get by somehow!
